<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "微软雅黑", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 25px;
        }
        .indent4{
            text-indent: 4em;
        }

        .email_content {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 50px auto;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: rgb(51, 153, 102);
        }

        .text-strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="email_content">
    <h1>Xingcloud</h1>
    <h4>亲爱的小伙伴，您好：</h4>

    <p>有客户申请开启项目，其信息如下：</p>
    <p class='indent4'><span class="text-strong">项目名称：</span> {{ service_name }} </p>
    <p class='indent4'><span class="text-strong">用户邮箱：</span> {{ email }} </p>
    <p class='indent4'><span class="text-strong">验证信息：</span> {{ verify_info }} </p>
    <p class='indent4'><span class="text-strong">申请时间：</span> {{ apply_date }} </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>